<H2><A CLASS=TITLE HREF="reviews/index.htm">Classical CD Reviews</A></H2><BR>
Each week we present a CD review. The focus is on the background behind the music, what was the composer's inspiration, and what was its influence, with an emphasis on a particular recording.<BR><BR>
