<H2><A CLASS=TITLE HREF="essential/index.htm">The Essential Classical Music Collection</A></H2><BR>
The huge range of music available is a bit daunting for the beginner. Here we present the top 10 classical works in each genre of symphonies, concertos, baroque, chamber, piano, opera, choral and twentieth century music. Not all will aggree with our selection but it certainly serves as a springboard for further exploration.</td></tr></table>

